SUMMARY:California Artisan Cheese Festival
DESCRIPTION:California’s premier cheese festival is back! The 20th Artisan Cheese Festival’s Sunday Marketplace brings together 100+ artisan cheese\, food\, wine\, beer\, and specialty producers under one roof. \nSample\, sip\, shop\, and meet the makers behind California’s thriving cheese scene. Each ticket includes a wineglass and insulated tote to fill with your favorite discoveries.
