SUMMARY:Lesbian & Queer Visibility: Three Short Films
DESCRIPTION:Lesbian & Queer Visibility: Three Short Films\nSunday\, March 22 • 1:00 p.m.\nOne Show Only!\nRialto Cinemas\, Sebastopol\nTickets and Trailers: https://rialtocinemas.com/coming-soon/ \nJoin us for an inspiring and fun afternoon of three short documentaries that honor Lesbian & Queer culture\, history\, and visibility.\nWe’re kicking things off with a high-energy screening to officially launch the first-ever and inclusive Sonoma County Dyke March & Lez-a-Palooza Street Fair—coming to the Santa Rosa Old Courthouse Square on June 21! \nAt the Rialto Films – come grab some swag\, snap a fun selfie\, raffles & door prizes\, and snag a custom wallet chain to level up your look. Every cent raised goes directly toward keeping this grassroots\, inclusive celebration loud and proud! \nFollow our us facebook.com/SonomaCountyDykeMarch\n@SoCoDykeMarch – on Instagram\nSoCoDykeMarch.org
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/lesbian-queer-visibility-three-short-films/
LOCATION:Rialto Cinemas Sebastopol\, 6868 McKinley St\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Film
GEO:38.4039;-122.823
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Rialto Cinemas Sebastopol 6868 McKinley St Sebastopol CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=6868 McKinley St:geo:-122.823,38.4039
END:VEVENT
