SUMMARY:Line Dancing at Hall of the Above
DESCRIPTION:Ready to kick up your boots and hit the dance floor?⁠ \nJoin us on Sunday\, February 22 and March 22\, (FOURTH Sunday of the Month this time) for a night of line dancing lessons and open dance. Whether you’re a seasoned dancer or stepping onto the floor for the first time\, they’ll guide you through every move. ⁠ \n⏰ Doors are at 4. Lessons start at 4:15! \n👢 Lessons and DJ by Grapevine Dance \n🎟️ $25 admission. Tickets at the link below\, or pay at the door. \n🕺 Kids 12 and under free. All skill levels welcome\, no partner required. \n🥖 We will have snacks and non-alcoholic drinks. \nSee you on the dance floor!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/line-dancing-at-hall-of-the-above-6/
