SUMMARY:The Bonafides at Murphy’s
DESCRIPTION:With some soulful saxophone and vocals\, settle in for an evening of New Orleans rhythm and blues.\nThe Bonafides sound is inspired by the great New Orleans pianists and the music and vibe of Treme\, the Bonafides keep the spirit and music of Longhair\, Booker\, Rebbenack\, and Cleary alive.\nNo matter what is on the set list\, we are sure you will leave a Bonafides show with a smile on your face and a happy tune in your step.
