SUMMARY:Karenna Slade - EP Release Party
DESCRIPTION:The Rise and Fall of a Midlife Queen! Come celebrate the debut solo album of Ukulele-Cabaret artist\, Karenna Slade.\nEP: The Rise and Fall of a Midlife Queen! \nThe evening will be chock full of performances dedicated to the Divine Feminine\, celebrating all of it from the joy and grief\, to the absurd.\nKarenna Slade is a singer-songwriter blending years of stage experience in clown\, comedy\, theater\, and burlesque with her soulful power vocals creating a musical experience that’s described as Lady Gaga meets Tenacious D. \nJoin us for a bawdy\, hilarious\, joyful and real experience dedicated to all bad bitches and those who love them. \nWebsite\nWww.karennaslade.com \nYou Tube @karennaslademusic\nhttps://youtube.com/@karennaslademusic?si=ULSN0I0x1uN3Sx_B \nDoors at 5pm. Show at 6pm.\nTickets $18 advance\, $25 at the door. \nOur kitchen is open and serving our All New Menu for events with 60 or more presale tickets.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/karenna-slade-ep-release-party/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Karenna-Slade.jpg
