SUMMARY:Bachata St. Patrick's at The Vintage Space
DESCRIPTION:Step Into a Night of Luck\, Dance\, and Emerald Enchantment!\nThis March\, join us for a high-energy St. Patrick’s Bachata Party you won’t want to miss!\nDress to impress in your best green\, gold\, and festive flair—think emerald tones\, shamrocks\, sparkling accents\, flowing fabrics\, sleek suits\, dresses\, Celtic-inspired touches\, or anything that brings that lucky charm energy. Whether you arrive in classic elegance or playful St. Paddy’s spirit\, you’ll be ready to light up the dance floor all night long! \nWe’re excited to welcome Emma back as your guide for the evening! She’ll lead a Bachata class designed to boost your confidence\, polish your style\, and get you comfortable on the dance floor—perfect for bringing that lively\, feel-good energy into every dance.\nGot a birthday in March? You’re in luck! March birthdays get in FREE—come celebrate and bring that birthday magic to the party!\nDJ Edge is back\, spinning an irresistible mix of Bachata\, Salsa\, and Cumbia\, keeping the dance floor packed and the energy flowing all night long under festive green lights and shamrock-inspired décor\nDoors Open: 7:30 PM \nClass Starts: 8:00 PM \nSocial Dancing Until: 1:00 AM\nEnjoy festive drink specials inspired by Irish flair—crafted to match the bold\, bright\, and lucky vibes of the night
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/bachata-st-patricks-at-the-vintage-space/
LOCATION:Vintage Space at The Flamingo Resort\, 2777 Fourth St.\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Other
GEO:38.45182;-122.68916
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Vintage Space at The Flamingo Resort 2777 Fourth St. Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=2777 Fourth St.:geo:-122.68916,38.45182
END:VEVENT
