SUMMARY:Pro Jam with Daniel Castro
DESCRIPTION:Blues guitarist Daniel Castro brings his warm\, soulful style back to The California!\nBlues guitarist Daniel Castro plays original songs and blues classics with a warm\, soulful style that recalls the blues greats Albert King\, B.B. King and Albert Collins.Daniel Castro learned his craft in the South Central L.A. blues clubs alongside “Mighty Mouth” Delmar Evans\, before recording and touring with artists including Small Faces singer-bassist Ronnie Lane. In 1995\, he formed The Daniel Castro Band\, releasing two albums under that name. He now plays regularly with bassist Johnny Yu and drummer David Perper. \nDoors open at 5pm Show Starts at 6pm. Tickets $15 online. $18 at door. $12 for members.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/pro-jam-with-daniel-castro/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
